# Agent-context stub + internal-companion-repo sentinels.
# Operational + spec context lives in github.com/khiip-ai/internal,
# loaded at session start via the gitignored CLAUDE.md stub.
# Pre-commit hook + CI path-guard + CODEOWNERS + GitHub push protection
# enforce this boundary; this gitignore is a soft outer layer.
/CLAUDE.md
/_internal/
/khiip-internal/
